    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "29. Jehoiachin … did eat … continually before him—According to an ancient usage in Eastern courts, had a seat at the royal table on great days, and had a stated provision granted him for the maintenance of his exiled court.   ",
        "children": []
      }
